# Direct (top-level) dependencies for Moodito — human-edited source of truth.
#
# The pinned, hash-locked install set lives in requirements.txt, which is
# GENERATED from this file. Do not edit requirements.txt by hand.
#
# Regenerate after changing anything here:
#
#   uv pip compile requirements.in \
#       --universal --python-version 3.11 --generate-hashes \
#       -o requirements.txt
#
# Moodito is a macOS-only menu bar app. rumps and pyobjc are macOS-only and
# their build scripts call /usr/bin/sw_vers, so guard them with a platform
# marker to keep the set resolvable on non-macOS tooling.
